title: [Marble Springs, Cobbled Path]
description: The dark expanse of the river can be glimpsed through a copse of slender ash trees to the south, its slow-moving waters casting occasional flashes of light from the bright sun overhead.  Barely visible through the tightly clustered woods, a short stone dock juts out into the river, a small wooden skiff resting next to its sturdy frame.
